summary:
David Tennant and Michael Sheen star in the Good Omens official trailer. 

With Armageddon just days away, the armies of Heaven...
caption:
David Tennant and Michael Sheen star in the Good Omens official trailer.

With Armageddon just days away, the armies of Heaven and Hell are amassing and The Four Horsemen are ready to ride. Aziraphale, an angel, and Crowley, a demon, agree to join forces to find the missing Anti-Christ and to stop the war that will end everything. Based on the best-selling novel by Terry Pratchett and Neil Gaiman, Good Omens follows an unlikely duo and their quest to save the world. 

Worldwide premiere on Amazon Prime on May 31st 2019

summary: Good Omens Trailer Thee angel Aziraphale (Michael Sheen) and the demon Crowley (David Tennant) are two unlikely friends trying...
caption:
Good Omens Trailer

Thee angel Aziraphale (Michael Sheen) and the demon Crowley (David Tennant) are two unlikely friends trying to stop the coming Armageddon. After all, they’ve grown quite fond of the Earth. Oh, and someone has misplaced the child Anti-Christ, so that’s a problem.

Good Omens, based on the novel by Neil Gaiman and Terry Pratchett, hits Amazon Prime on May 31, 2019.

body:
1st Look: ‘Good Omens’ Full Trailer

The casting is perfect in the new Amazon Prime trailer for Good Omens .

Leading the cast are two recognizable faces.  David Tennant (Doctor Who) is Crowley, a demon who did not so much fall as saunter vaguely downwards, who loves scalding-hot showers and driving his Bentley far too fast.  As his opposite number, Aziraphale,…
